oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mae Axton interview - Biff Collie
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recording of an interview with Mae Axton (performer), conducted by Biff Collie. Main topic of the conversation is Elvis Presley.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Biff Collie asks questions about Elvis -- Mae Axton talks about liking Elvis best in his glitter suits and black jump suits -- Axton talks about liking Elvis' songs My Way and Don't Be Cruel the most -- Axton talks about her favorite Elvis record being his gold number one record -- Axton talks about her favorite live Elvis performance experiences -- Axton talks about what the public does not know about Elvis -- Axton tells a story about Elvis paying for a little girls eye operation (incomplete)
